➜广东诗人小隐：一叶落．秋（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/416289829_100115135	35411
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200903/c888890dcdf44a589ef292ce6150d662.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一叶落．秋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一叶落，秋风索。恰如碎画正斑驳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最伤独影人，人离情生薄，情生薄。负气谁担着？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200903/317d44ccb51742bdb82e9b59428bb680.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>秋思</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋声萧瑟动离情，一夜秋风满客城。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不尽相思无用处，愁心相寄到天明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200903/0032a7a6021a411ea038d00b85601bb3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
