➜湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：写在中元节
http://www.sohu.com/a/416290711_100115135	35724
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200903/9de72b2850da42dba35e4539dae8cf67.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>写在中元节</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣(武汉)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今夜幽萤舞成朵朵小菊花</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一盏盏烛灯闪闪，阴间的路不黑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中元节的夜焰燃起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">敬先祖，轻声唤回天堂的魂灵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我已放出纸蝴蝶分发冥钱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>乘烟穿雾跳过火焰山</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我已送出包袱，祭拜已逝的亲人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>捎去的是泪雨洗过的真情</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋风顾盼，能听到落叶声</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可我听不到回应</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我思念的先祖呀，来无踪去无影</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只留巴望的眼在人间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>写于2020年9月2日晚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200903/f2f52b79ba484960a36f68c47e95a668.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
